remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="64368-102">设计器它们自己序列化为代码通过搜索对象的实时属性值，并为代码生成这些值的引擎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-102">Designers serialize themselves to code through an engine that searches through the live property values of objects and generates those values as code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64368-103">例如，因此，一个按钮的文本将采用以下格式生成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-103">So, for example, the text of a button is generated in the following format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
this.okButton.Text = "OK";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="64368-104">此方案的局限性之一是很难从其他位置检索的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-104">One of the limitations of this scheme is that it is difficult to retrieve a property from another location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64368-105">例如，它很难发出以下格式的代码，因为只能代码生成器可以依赖于是属性中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-105">For example, it is very difficult to emit code in the following format, because the only thing the code generator can rely on is the value in the property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
this.titleLabel.Text = this.Text;  
```  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="64368-106"><xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService>简化了另一个位置中的属性值的检索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-106">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> simplifies retrieval of a property value from another location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64368-107">设计器可以访问此服务以指定该一个成员分配的另一个的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-107">A designer can access this service to dictate that one member is assigned the value of another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64368-108">生成代码时，此类关系搜索代码生成器并如果代码生成器找到两个成员之间的关系，则它会发出关系的代码而不是搜索的属性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-108">The code generator searches for such relationships when generating code, and if a relationship between two members is found the code generator, it emits code for the relationship rather than searching for the property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64368-109">使用前面的文本分配作为示例，下面的代码示例演示设计时代码用于建立关系。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64368-109">Using the previous text assignment as an example, the following code example shows design time code used to establish a relationship.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object titleLabel, form;  
PropertyDescriptor titleLabelText = TypeDescriptor.GetProperties(titleLabel)["Text"];  
PropertyDescriptor formText = TypeDescriptor.GetProperties(form)["Text"];  
MemberRelationshipService ms = GetService(typeof(MemberRelationshipService);  
ms[titleLabel, titleLabelText] = new MemberRelationship(form, formText);  
```
